---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title="Why Choose Us?" description="Learn about the key benefits of New Leaf Academy's personalized tutoring services." />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1>Why Choose Us?</h1>
			<p>
				At New Leaf Academy, we believe every student has the potential to shine. We understand that in a traditional classroom, it’s easy for individual needs to be overlooked. That’s why we do more than just teach; we bring a fresh energy to learning, building confidence, inspiring curiosity, and tailoring our approach to fit each unique learner. Our commitment is to create a supportive and dynamic environment where your child can truly succeed, on their own terms.
			</p>
			<h2>Our Commitment to Your Success:</h2>
			<ul>
				<li>
					<strong>Safety-First Approach:</strong> Your child's safety is our top priority. Every New Leaf Academy tutor undergoes a comprehensive vetting process, including an enhanced DBS check and thorough interviews, so you can have complete peace of mind.
				</li>
				<li>
					<strong>Proven Results & Expert Tutors:</strong> We have a strong track record of helping students achieve top grades. Our specialist tutors are not only experts in their subjects but are also dedicated to helping you succeed.
				</li>
				<li>
					<strong>Empathetic & Personalized Learning:</strong> We have extensive experience helping students with neurodivergence, SEND, dyslexia, dyscalculia, autism, and ADHD. Our tutors build genuine rapport and trust, ensuring every session is a supportive space where students feel understood and confident.
				</li>
				<li>
					<strong>Freedom from the Classroom Clock:</strong> We break free from the rigid timetables and fixed curriculum of traditional schooling. Unconstrained by a one-size-fits-all approach, our passionate tutors adapt every lesson to the student's immediate needs. Whether it's tackling a tough homework problem or exploring a topic in greater depth, our teaching is always relevant, effective, and perfectly paced for them.
				</li>
				<li>
					<strong>Fostering Lifelong Confidence:</strong> Our goal extends beyond exam results. Through energetic and supportive mentoring, we work to transform a student's relationship with learning, turning anxiety and self-doubt into curiosity and unshakeable confidence that will serve them long after their time with us.
				</li>
				<li>
					<strong>Collaborative Parent Partnership:</strong> We believe in keeping you in the loop. You'll receive regular, detailed feedback on your child's progress, including areas of strength and opportunities for growth, ensuring we're working together as a team.
				</li>
				<li>
					<strong>Modern & Effective Teaching:</strong> As a young and energetic team, we are passionate about using the latest research-driven strategies. We use a blend of fresh teaching methods, cutting-edge techniques, and the newest technology to create engaging lessons that make learning feel relevant and exciting.
				</li>
				<li>
					<strong>Free, No-Obligation Consultation:</strong> We want to ensure we're the perfect fit for your family. That's why we offer a complimentary consultation to discuss your child's needs, answer your questions, and introduce you to our approach before you make any commitment.
				</li>
			</ul>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
<style>
	:root {
		--primary-color: var(--accent);
		--text-color: var(--accent);
		--card-bg-color: #f9f9f9;
        --box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
	}

	body {
		font-family: sans-serif;
		line-height: 1.6;
		color: var(--accent);
		margin: 0;
		padding: 0;
	}

	main {
		color: var(--accent);
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 2em auto;
		padding: 0 1em;
		box-sizing: border-box;
	}

	h1 {
		color: var(--accent);
		font-size: clamp(1.8em, 5vw, 2.5em);
		text-align: center;
	}

	h2 {
		color: var(--accent);
		font-size: clamp(1.5em, 4vw, 1.8em);
		margin-top: 2em;
	}

	p {
		color: var(--accent);
		font-size: clamp(1em, 2vw, 1.1em);
	}

	ul {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
	}

	li {
		margin-bottom: 1.5em;
		line-height: 1.5;
		background-color: var(--card-bg-color);
		padding: 1.5em;
		border-radius: 10px;
		box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
		word-break: break-word; /* Force long words to wrap */
	}

	li strong {
		display: block;
		font-size: clamp(1.1em, 2.5vw, 1.2em);
		margin-bottom: 0.5em;
	}
</style>

